es/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"aa9b8dfd71b7fe38bdeac5f6163a3d196dc37344","tid":1553781,"uid":282587,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-08T17:22:27.000Z","msg":"避孕套，林鄭攪佢全國攪炒，林鄭用完即棄恰如其份。"},{"pid":"0e534d44dc5fcc28b37fce494ef8717067eb6827","tid":1553781,"uid":123914,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"c418597c0b014e34008e4148a68999a4210ba48a","tid":1553781,"uid":247180,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-08T17:11:55.000Z","msg":"叫佢哋過街老鼠 暫時見過係最work"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-08T17:29:30.000Z","msg":"岩 撚好再嗌黑社會啦 冇用架"},{"pid":"a3ebeb3dcee8c8ece45dc03549cf9f33ecf02520","tid":1553781,"uid":255347,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"0e534d44dc5fcc28b37fce494ef8717067eb6827","tid":1553781,"uid":123914,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"c418597c0b014e34008e4148a68999a4210ba48a","tid":1553781,"uid":247180,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-08T17:11:55.000Z","msg":"叫佢哋過街老鼠 暫時見過係最work"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-08T17:29:30.000Z","msg":"岩 撚好再嗌黑社會啦 冇用架"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-08T17:44:49.000Z","msg":"人少嗌好易比狗拉<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/escape.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e3b325252c57e02a14b7cb1d6c55e6bc53210b4a","tid":1553781,"uid":216789,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-08T17:46:00.000Z","msg":"<strong>慎防黑惡勢力蔓延禍港，提防本地非法操縱妓女賣淫集團</strong><br />\n<br />\n鑒於近日有無辜香港市民慘遭黑勢力人仕襲擊，現懇切呼籲各香港市民不論男女，請慎防本地非法操縱妓女賣淫集團，保障自身安全，萬事小心，<strong><span style=\"color: red;\">切忌助長黑惡勢力氣焰</span></strong>"},{"pid":"40ed22d9940928deb04591465c8477990d9b7815","tid":1553781,"uid":53870,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-08T17:49:35.000Z","msg":"係佢地門口燒野擺祭品等佢地清"},{"pid":"e0fdea4f320c071990a061441d5fbcda7fdd1eb9","tid":1553781,"uid":123713,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-08T17:57:09.000Z","msg":"係敵人面前憤怒<br />\n只會令對方覺得得戚<br />\n<br />\n有時候譏諷比憤怒更有效<br />\n用一個<span style=\"color: teal;\"><strong>&rdquo;我地香港人而家係擺明睇唔起你地&rdquo;</strong></span>既姿態笑尻呢班<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><strong><span style=\"color: red;\"><br />\n收納稅人錢 再打納稅人<br />\n讀唔成書走去做打手<br />\n未出學堂就比人洗撚左腦仲自命正義<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n呢一刻人工8萬蚊個月 <br />\n遲早比老解2000蚊人工取代既中共棄卒<br />\n冇錯 係$2000啊柒頭 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n去到邊都噓聲不斷 <br />\n得班收$300既大媽專程係支那落黎支持你地<br />\n係香港就斷六親<br />\n個仔返學都要保鏢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n你地究竟羞唔羞家？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n有咩事共產黨只會搵人斬9死你地吸引眼球咋，寫咗遺書準備好瞓浩園未啊condom仔？<br />\n<br />\n唉對唔住 好似深左少少<br />\n你只係一隻連醜字都唔撚識寫既毅進狗<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n</span></strong></span>"},{"pid":"02475fa2f2d67897255c677e5d4cbafa14320f00","tid":1553781,"uid":123914,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"a3ebeb3dcee8c8ece45dc03549cf9f33ecf02520","tid":1553781,"uid":255347,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"0e534d44dc5fcc28b37fce494ef8717067eb6827","tid":1553781,"uid":123914,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"c418597c0b014e34008e4148a68999a4210ba48a","tid":1553781,"uid":247180,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-08T17:11:55.000Z","msg":"叫佢哋過街老鼠 暫時見過係最work"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-08T17:29:30.000Z","msg":"岩 撚好再嗌黑社會啦 冇用架"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-08T17:44:49.000Z","msg":"人少嗌好易比狗拉<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/escape.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-08T18:55:49.000Z","msg":"人少嗌咩都被狗拉架啦 自己醒排啦<br />\n人多就緊係大大力屌 佢地越勞氣我地越要開心<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">記住係撚狗</span></span> 唔係屌狗 佢地見到我地咁勞氣反而開心"},{"pid":"28838bccbb6ca4c466e99437d11b5b2943e91306","tid":1553781,"uid":291167,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-08T19:11:24.000Z","msg":"我建議大家嗌多一個口號：「解散警隊」"},{"pid":"fc5a464a4ee9ea5d06d8db067045333c5e1c28a0","tid":1553781,"uid":255347,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-08T23:48:28.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"6334beeae065e3b12d24fb9b8893747692bdd549","tid":1553781,"uid":54303,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"4616567d6ef8aceddb1eefb6b221f66b15f95a0b","tid":1553781,"uid":155902,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-09-08T17:12:11.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/censored.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-08T23:49:50.000Z","msg":"只有活捉先有證據證明係公安扮"},{"pid":"50a3f8eed024a3b4b898c4bc769a22e690df14ee","tid":1553781,"uid":255347,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-09T00:19:45.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"3bf5f84528b6ad4cbde194325b811baa1dc85257","tid":1553781,"uid":89873,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-09T00:40:45.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"43d3bddd188019ef6f9a19a034d3dab5dacb01c7","tid":1553781,"uid":267212,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"4616567d6ef8aceddb1eefb6b221f66b15f95a0b","tid":1553781,"uid":155902,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-09-08T17:12:11.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/censored.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-09T00:52:51.000Z","msg":"圍佢，斷正就無得唔認"},{"pid":"8df6d327b572cbcb34f0afa50a92ca94043dea58","tid":1553781,"uid":77145,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-09T00:56:30.000Z","msg":"可能係聽唔明<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: large;\